com.mcc.ul
Class Status

java.lang.Object
  com.mcc.ul.Status

public class Status
extends java.lang.Object

This class returns the status of a DAQ operation when called with getStatus(). The status reported will be associated with the subsystem used to instantiate the class, for example (AiDevice or DioDevice).
